primary.reasoning: Button #2 ('Explore AI Apps') has a dark background (#0B0F19) with white text, making it stand out prominently. The action-oriented text 'Explore AI Apps' suggests a primary call-to-action, encouraging users to engage with the site's offerings.

secondary.reasoning: Button #1 ('Getting started') has a blue background (#E5E7EB) and serves as a secondary action, guiding users to begin their journey with the platform. It complements the primary button without overshadowing it.
